description:
This is the award for our GIVEAWAY SERIES 🎁  of 25 FREE Soonacity🏙️ cribs!

The 25 giveaway winners will be granted with this award and badge. They'll then be able to mint one crib from our OG collection "Soonacity🏙️" for free.

The free OG cribs will be randomly minted on a separate Soonacity🏙️ collection [FREE Edition] here on Soonaverse (still to be announced).

[INFO]

- LIKE & RETWEET our giveaway series posts on twitter 
- FOLLOW us on twitter
- JOIN our Soonaverse space
- PARTICIPATE in this award ("Cribs Giveaway 25")
- PROVIDE your twitter name in the award participation contact box!
- IF YOU FORGOT IT then change your Soonaverse name to your twitter name or provide your twitter link in your Soonaverse profile.
name: Cribs Giveaway 25
